SESSION.DESCRIPTION: This mapping loads the stging table STG_MX_ITEM data to the SLBA_ITEM target table.
SESSION.NAME: s_m_SLBA_ITEM_LOAD_MX

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Post SQL
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
UPDATE INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL SET TGT_VAL=( SELECT count(*) FROM SLBA_ITEM WHERE UPDATE_TIMESTAMP= (SELECT MAX(MAP_RUN_DT) FROM INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_DFLT_SLBA_ITEM_MX' AND MAP_RUN_DT <=SYSDATE)) WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_DFLT_SLBA_ITEM_MX' AND MAP_RUN_DT=(SELECT MAX(MAP_RUN_DT) FROM INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_DFLT_SLBA_ITEM_MX' AND MAP_RUN_DT <=SYSDATE ) ;
UPDATE INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL SET STATUS_YN = (CASE WHEN SRC_VAL = TGT_VAL THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END ) WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_DFLT_SLBA_ITEM_MX' AND MAP_RUN_DT=(SELECT MAX(MAP_RUN_DT) FROM INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_DFLT_SLBA_ITEM_MX' AND MAP_RUN_DT <=SYSDATE );
